Fulfillment Policy

Fulfillment Policy

In case of any questions, contact us directly on contact@nathanfx.com email address or on https://t.me/+ykp8HWnzE1YxZDA8 Telegram Communicator.


• Customer can unsubscribe to the nathanfx service at any 6me, then the next fee will not be charged. To cancel subscription, Customer has to log in to Customer’s account on this website (https://nathanfx/my-account/sumo-subscriptions) go to „MY SUBSCRIPTIONS”, choose the subscription and click „CANCEL”. After the Subscription is cancelled, Customer will receive a confirmation email on the registered email address. In case of any problems, contact us on contact@nathanfx.com email address or on https://t.me/+ykp8HWnzE1YxZDA8 Telegram Communicator.

• After purchasing nathanfx service, Customer will receive an email with a joining link which gives access to purchased service.

• Customer can ask for a money refund within 14 days after purchasing the Nathan FX.com service. Customer needs to write a request, via the contact form on this website – (https://nathanfx/#contact) with the reason and order number. Request will be considered within 3 working days, and Customer will be informed vie email after the refund is proceeded. From refunded amount, refund fees may be deducted. Refunds beyond these 14 days period are at our sole discretion. After the refund is proceeded, Customer access to nathanfx service is blocked. For more details, visit our Terms and conditions and Privacy policy.

RR Group, address: Dabrowskiego 77a, Poznan 60-529, PL
